2
00:00:12.164 --> 00:00:14.165
<v ->Many people still view meditation</v>

3
00:00:14.165 --> 00:00:16.334
as a spiritual practice that's optional

4
00:00:16.334 --> 00:00:18.403
while at the same time turning to psychics

5
00:00:18.403 --> 00:00:22.307
as intermediaries to receive reflections of our own truths.

6
00:00:22.307 --> 00:00:24.209
This doesn't make sense anymore.

7
00:00:24.209 --> 00:00:26.678
If there were ever a time to access our own truth

8
00:00:26.678 --> 00:00:29.281
to navigate through life, the time would be now,

9
00:00:29.281 --> 00:00:32.950
and we can't do it without a clear and connected mind.

10
00:00:32.950 --> 00:00:35.720
Sarah McLean has been teaching meditation for decades

11
00:00:35.720 --> 00:00:37.288
and has some poignant thoughts

12
00:00:37.288 --> 00:00:39.974
as to its value in our lives.

