694
00:27:40.245 --> 00:27:42.313
Simply sitting down with your eyes closed,

695
00:27:42.313 --> 00:27:44.082
turning your cellphone off,

696
00:27:44.082 --> 00:27:47.385
planning, I'd say, to start,

