00:27:47.385 --> 00:27:50.655
10 to 20 minutes, I'd love to say twice a day,

698
00:27:50.655 --> 00:27:52.924
but even if you do it once a day,

699
00:27:52.924 --> 00:27:55.694
closing the eyes, planning the 10 minutes,

700
00:27:55.694 --> 00:27:58.230
sitting down focusing on your breath initially,

701
00:27:58.230 --> 00:27:59.764
relaxing the body,

702
00:27:59.764 --> 00:28:02.700
paying attention to the way the body feels,

703
00:28:02.700 --> 00:28:04.970
then bringing your attention to the breath,

704
00:28:04.970 --> 00:28:07.138
and then you can start that mantra,

705
