I suggested "so" on the inhale,

706
00:28:09.207 --> 00:28:10.842
"hum" on the exhale,

707
00:28:10.842 --> 00:28:12.410
and simply just paying attention

708
00:28:12.410 --> 00:28:14.746
to the sound of the sounds.

709
00:28:14.746 --> 00:28:18.149
And you can time yourself by looking at a clock.

710
00:28:18.149 --> 00:28:21.086
Basically though, I do suggest people time themselves

711
00:28:21.086 --> 00:28:22.821
and to stick with the amount of time

712
00:28:22.821 --> 00:28:24.889
