713
00:28:24.889 --> 00:28:28.026
And one of the most important things I like to say is

714
00:28:28.026 --> 00:28:31.796
at the very end of it, sit with your eyes closed

715
00:28:31.796 --> 00:28:34.432
and just in the silence for a minute or two

