00:29:10.802 --> 00:29:13.139
And it's different than what you're used to.

735
00:29:13.139 --> 00:29:16.809
We're all used to being either awake, asleep, or dreaming.

736
00:29:16.809 --> 00:29:18.610
But when we meditate, we're literally

737
00:29:18.610 --> 00:29:20.379
in a fourth state of consciousness,

