00:33:36.074 --> 00:33:37.134
<v Regina>Yeah, you got to get out and work</v>

852
00:33:37.134 --> 00:33:40.271
and get on with my life, but it's very beautiful.

853
00:33:40.271 --> 00:33:41.973
Any final thoughts on this?

854
00:33:41.973 --> 00:33:45.077
I mean you've given a lot of really practical information

855
00:33:45.077 --> 00:33:47.512
because people do think, "Oh, I'll wait 'til later.

856
00:33:47.512 --> 00:33:48.346
"I'm intimidated.

